snippet.title: original song: “cold"
snippet.description:
Hey lovelies, here’s another original song I wrote awhile ago, in February, called cold. Hope you enjoy❤️

Lyrics:

I’m tired of being cold all the time
I said I’m tired of being cold all the time 
would you be warm for me?
valentine

the leaves on the trees turning red in the Fall
are like hearts of mercy that fall 
but they ain’t falling for me
cause there ain’t no tree 

I’m tired of being cold all the time 
I said I’m tired of being cold all the time
would you be warm for me?
valentine 

and when that water freeze to ice
but that river keeping a flowin’ despite 
cause as cold as I may be 
I never freeze 

and I said I’m tired of being cold all the time 
yeah I said I’m tired of being cold all the time 
so this February baby
would you be mine?

Follow me on the gram! @herhabitschannel
